                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Hybrid Models</h3>
                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">10 - 12 Years</div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
